data.description: Are you looking for more space? Look no further! Come check out this 4 bedroom, 3 full bath, manufactured home on a sprawling 2.5 acres! Sit back and enjoy the slower pace of life outside the busy city but still inside the Noble school district. Here you will be delighted to find fully fenced acreage, as well as 2 storage buildings, 1 converted and insulated office building, 1 metal, stand-in, horse barn and a chicken coop! The home itself boasts 2,280 sq ft, four spacious bedrooms, three full bathrooms, along with two living areas! If space is what you need, don't wait, schedule your showing today!
